---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About -- Roderick.Dev" activeNav="about">
  <div class="content-pad">

    <span class="page-label">About</span>

    <div class="intro-row">
      <div class="intro-text">
        <p class="lede">I'm an economist and AI systems practitioner. I run <strong>Flamelit</strong>, where I lead consulting for data science, AI architecture, and AI strategy work across government, healthcare, and industry. I'm also Affiliate Faculty at the Raymond A. Mason School of Business at William &amp; Mary.</p>
      </div>
      <img class="headshot" src="/headshot.jpg" alt="Thomas Roderick">
    </div>

    <div class="body-section">
      <p>Before consulting I spent five years at <strong>JP Morgan Chase</strong> as a lead data scientist in retail finance, two years as a senior data science director for clinical and population health at <strong>Parkland Center for Clinical Innovation</strong> (where I continue to support as an executive-in-residence), and hold a PhD in Economics from UT Austin. My research has appeared in <em>Information Systems Research</em>, <em>INFORMS Journal on Computing</em>, <em>New England Journal of Medicine: Catalyst</em>, and <em>DESRIST</em> conference proceedings.</p>

      <p>Outside of work I play soccer and spend time in the woodcraft workshop. This site is where I write about the work -- the methods, the failures, the occasional finding worth sharing.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="links-row">
      <a href="/writing/">Writing</a>
      <a href="/cv/">CV</a>
      <a href="mailto:tom@flamelit.tech">tom@flamelit.tech</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</Base>

<style>
.intro-row {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 2.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
}
.intro-text {
  flex: 1;
}
.intro-text .lede {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}
.headshot {
  width: 160px;
  height: 160px;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: 2px;
  border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .intro-row {
    flex-direction: column-reverse;
  }
  .headshot {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
  }
}
.page-label {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: var(--muted);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  display: block;
}
.lede {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 350;
  line-height: 1.65;
  color: var(--text);
}
.body-section {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.4rem;
  max-width: 60ch;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}
.body-section p {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: var(--text);
}
.body-section strong {
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--text);
}
.links-row {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  align-items: center;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
  padding-top: 1.5rem;
}
.links-row a {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}
</style>
